modName: My Personal ENB Config Rustic and Atmospheric
summary: A Rustic looking ENB series config.
descriptionHtml:
---TESTED ON THE FOLLOWING SPEC---
Radeon 6950 2gb
i7 2600k 4.5GHZ
8GB DDR3
WIN7 Ultimate 64 Bit

REUPLOADED EVERYTHING WITHOUT SOURCE FILES DUE TO COPYRIGHT ISSUES!!! READ INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS TO GET THIS TO WORK!

Hello, this is my first file really, I\'ve been a lurker for some time and decided to share my personal ENB config to the community. 

I personally enjoy it, you may not like it- it is simply a matter of taste. I don\'t need anyone telling me how \'bad\' it is. As it is merely a matter of preference. If you like it, I\'m glad you could have it and enjoy it as I do.

<---WHAT THIS IS--->
A Rustic Config that adds to the atmosphere of skyrim. Nights may have a greenish or bluish tint depending the on the weather. Daytime has a orange-ish tint, and the colors are much more vivid and clear- not like vanilla skyrim, where everything was bland and dull. This really enchances the atmopshere. (For me.) And it may do the same for you.

<---WHAT THIS IS NOT--->
This is not a realistic config, nights are not impossible to see in due to lack of light, you can still see generally clear, shadows however are indeed deep, and it may or may not be hard to see in those, but this by no means realistic.
----------------------------------------------

If you dont like something, download the ENB customizer and sort it out yourself, it really helps, and has helped in the creation of this config, hats off to the modder!
---------------------------------------------
I hope you enjoy this config, have fun!
---------------------------------------------
---INSTALLATION---
Just drop the contents of the RAR in your root directory, if you got a current skyrim ENB config, back it up. If you don\'t have software to open RAR files go grab winrar from here. Copy the address into your address bar.

http://www.rarlab.com/

 After you install those contents, go to boris vorontsov\'s website and get the ENBinjector.exe. It can be found here. Copy and paste the link into your address bar. Drop this into your root directory as well.

http://www.enbdev.com/download_injector_generic.htm
---------------------------------------------
UNINSTALLATION
You dont really need to uninstall since this is injector based and is only present while running the injector- but if you need to, just look back at your .rar file. Look at its contents, and just delete the files you see in the rar archive that correspond to your actual installation.
---------------------------------------------
HOW TO USE
Run ENBinjector.exe before launching skyrim, afterwards just launch skyrim while running the injector to get it to work.
Reccommendations- I highly reccommend more snow and more rain mods, they really add to the atmosphere of the config, especially during storms, the green fog at some points really gives a sinister/Atmopsheric look to skyrim.
----------------------------------------------------
IMAGES
Sadly im having some difficulty with images so I am forced to redirect you to my xfire photos page. Here are some images!
